strings.Value: "Get out of my way. I want Nyrissa and I will get to her."
[Attack] "Nyrissa will pay for everything, and so will her servants!"

{n}The Horned Hunter salutes you.{/n} "Ah, the {mf|king|queen} of the sand castle. You made it? After defeating the Jabberwock... I have to admit — I'm impressed! But what will you do now? Pick up the silly little bard's body?"
{n}The Horned Hunter shrugs, then nods at the breathless body on the floor.{/n} "She thought she could trick the mistress. Well, she's not the first one, and she won't be the last."
"No, silly creature. It's Nyrissa who wants you. You are the last grain of dust that will fall in the Apology. And I will bring this grain to her!"
"You won't find answers, you'll find death. It's time to fill the mistress's cup!'
{n}Octavia's eyes are filled with tears, but she angrily wipes them away with a jerking motion.{/n} "You'll pay for this, you hear me?!"
{n}Amiri's face is like a stone mask. She almost growls as she speaks.{/n} "Hold on, carrion. Better yet — call your mistress. You both have a lot to answer for!"
"No, no… dear Linzi – why?! I feel like I've lost another sister…" {n}Kalikke covers her face with her hands.{/n}
